note","text":"同根 prospector n. 探勘者；采矿者"},{"type":"entry","text":"reef /riːf/ n. 矿脉","headword":"reef"},{"type":"text","text":"rock salt 岩盐"},{"type":"entry","text":"shale /ʃeɪl/ n. 页岩；泥板岩","headword":"shale"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 oil shale 油页岩"}]}]}